STATE
v.
Kenneth Wayne WILLIAMS. No. 105P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 6, 2006. Scott T. Stroud, Assistant Attorney General, Howard S. Boney, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st day of March 2006 by Defendant to Stay the Mandate:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of March 2006."
